headline: Cincinnati Financial Corporation Expands Board With Appointment of Independent Director
summary: Cincinnati Financial Corporation (Nasdaq: CINF) – Cincinnati Financial Corporation's board of directors added a 14th seat, appointing Edward S. Wilkins, CPA, to the board and as a member of its audit committee, effective immediately.
